reviewText: This was not a video at all, but rather an interactive something I can't describe.
My Grandson loved the movie, i explained to him I had watched the same animated movie when i was young.....
Amazon Rocks! I use to love this movie growing up! I am so glad amazon had it. Can't wait to share with my kids!

This is used for the letter U and works great.  The kids see this movie the first time in their lives when they see it at school.  They love it, and they get really involved in the little duckling life.  Good for the letter U, good for feelings, good for accepting who you are.

This wasn't the one I had 20 years ago for my kids, so I was dissapointed! It was
a different version of it and I didn't like this one. The quality wasn't that good either.
